Invention:  Writing
Year:       3200
Inventor:   Sumerians
Country:    Mesopotamia
Category:   Communication
Description:Cuneiform marks in clay tablets
Impact:     Enabled civilization-scale organization and history

Invention:  Transistor
Year:       1947
Inventor:   Bardeen/Brattain/Shockley
Country:    USA
Category:   Electronics
Description:Semiconductor switch replacing vacuum tubes
Impact:     Foundation of all modern electronics; miniaturization

Invention:  Printing Press
Year:       1440
Inventor:   Gutenberg
Country:    Germany
Category:   Communication
Description:Movable metal type for mass printing
Impact:     Democratized knowledge; enabled Reformation and science

